      "title": "Minister meets CEB Engineers",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Minister of Power and Energy said that he met with the Senior Engineers Union of the Ceylon Electricity Board (CEB) on Wednesday (17).",
        "He said that they had a productive discussion regarding the restructuring plans.",
        "They had pledged their commitment to reforms & renewable energy plans, and gave their proposals & requested to expedite them.",
        "The Senior Engineers Union supported the last CEB Act amendment as well, tweeted the Minister."
      ],
